<subSubSection pageId="78" pageNumber="355" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="78.[2016,2609,1720,2147]" pageId="78" pageNumber="355">
Taxonomic validity of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Merriam" authorityYear="1894" box="[2348,2464,1798,1831]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Hodomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="78" pageNumber="355" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Hodomys</taxonomicName>
has been widely reviewed; most authors consider it a valid genus. Four subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
